 and energy and resources industries he also has indepth experience in strategy enterprise risk management and regulatory affairs from his many years providing professional services to numerous major utilities his deep understanding of public utility markets and the breadth of experience he has gained from working with public companies make him a valuable resource to the group source california water service group on    sign up for equilar atlas and view gregory e aliffs full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like gregory e aliff more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in gregory e aliffs network and community follow changes in gregory e aliffs employment and moneyinmotion connect with gregory e aliff through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example gregory e aliff gregory e aliffs connections  sign up now to view gregory e aliffs  connections » thomas m krummel former board member california water service group richard p magnuson former lead independent director california water service group terry p bayer chief operating officer molina healthcare inc james m micali lead independent director sonoco products company maceo k sloan board member scana corporation peter c nelson former chairman of the board california water service group martin a kropelnicki president and chief executive officer california water service group edwin a guiles board member california water service group george a vera board member california water service group bonnie g hill board member california water service group popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thomas j lynch executive chairman te connectivity ltd john j kita evp and cfo a o smith elon r musk ceo and chairman tesla david j oconnor president and ceo the madison square garden company carl g annessa evp and coo hornbeck offshore services inc × claim 